Story: Test HTTP GET request to fetch data from an API
# STARTER - Basic HTTP client example showing GET requests

Given:
  api_url: String = "http://httpbin.org/get"
  response: String = ""
  status: Integer = 0

Step 1 → Fetch data from API
  Because: Testing HTTP GET functionality
  Effect: HTTP GET from api_url into response

Step 2 → Display response
  Because: Show what we received
  Effect: Print "Response: {response}"

Step 3 → Display status code
  Because: Check if request was successful
  Then: status becomes HTTP_STATUS
  Effect: Print "Status code: {status}"

End: Return response
  Because: Return the API response
